      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GARY INDIANA (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money five on end before a last start eighth (30.60) at this track. Better than last start and worth following up. SAVINA (3) produced a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 400m behind Jet Fuel (23.79) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. One of the better hopes. REBORN DESTINY (4) failed to come into contention last start after missing the jump at this track, but prior to that won by 2 lengths at this track (22.96) beating Bushland Boy in a Grade 5 on May 15. Worth following up. DOLLAR ROLEX (8) is a last-start placegetter who will have admirers.",
